{"tid":273810,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"減肥，以後都冇得食大快活早餐喇","createTime":"2017-06-07T00:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T09:03:43.000Z","uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"619acbaf99ef7cb9fc085b23b3a6fb24dba7e384","tid":273810,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T00:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞扒炒蛋蘿蔔糕<br />\n辣肉醬麵<br />\n凍奶茶<br />\n<br />\n已經戒左兩個月左右<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n76減到而家61-63<br />\n階段勝利目標係55<br />\n我自己想落到40-45"},{"pid":"d6455fd8a37f070718e33bc578eac3ad01246d71","tid":273810,"uid":13952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T00:57:41.000Z","msg":"大快活啲炒蛋好油 不過真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加油巴打我都減緊 依家改變緊食野方式<br />\n盡量早食最多&gt;午&gt;晚 另外早晚飲蘋果醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c83fed84dc9cd7ca366916aa21985a747a5cbe","tid":273810,"uid":13952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T00:58:15.000Z","msg":"巴打你係純戒口兩個月減左咁多？"},{"pid":"d445f279142071f703788c9ab8a684e4820b56ef","tid":273810,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T01:01:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大快活啲炒蛋好油 不過真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加油巴打我都減緊 依家改變緊食野方式<br />\n盡量早食最多&gt;午&gt;晚 另外早晚飲蘋果醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好香滑<br />\n雞扒好油不過連皮好好咬"},{"pid":"c4edf154e3f3da99f9cfecfda4145a3ac641cb02","tid":273810,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T01:03:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你係純戒口兩個月減左咁多？</blockquote><br />\n當我兩年前開始斷斷續續減啦<br />\n<br />\n我2013年中學畢業豬咁肥<br />\n<br />\n上年都好多人話我瘦左好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上年11月開始認真連續減到而家<br />\n76減到61-63<br />\n體脂肪都有減到不過仍然好高"},{"pid":"6beffbcdd4324693f015013efea9ae995db029f0","tid":273810,"uid":14349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T01:04:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞扒炒蛋蘿蔔糕<br />\n辣肉醬麵<br />\n凍奶茶<br />\n<br />\n已經戒左兩個月左右<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n76減到而家61-63<br />\n階段勝利目標係55<br />\n我自己想落到40-45</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無做運動？ 帶氧加重訓<br />\n<br />\n否則戒一世口，一食即反彈"},{"pid":"7e5d1728acc1145324f5603bc06014d5b39756ae","tid":273810,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T01:08:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞扒炒蛋蘿蔔糕<br />\n辣肉醬麵<br />\n凍奶茶<br />\n<br />\n已經戒左兩個月左右<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n76減到而家61-63<br />\n階段勝利目標係55<br />\n我自己想落到40-45</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無做運動？ 帶氧加重訓<br />\n<br />\n否則戒一世口，一食即反彈</blockquote><br />\n有做<br />\n帶氧連續半年喇<br />\n<br />\n重訓去gym我要計下個支出先<br />\n<br />\n上網搵到d好出名的大陸人寫的書<br />\n講家居健身，心諗得唔得嫁<br />\n果條友幾出名下"},{"pid":"fe4eed2df3e34bf9be978e424b3a4b5854caad11","tid":273810,"uid":92131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T01:49:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞扒炒蛋蘿蔔糕<br />\n辣肉醬麵<br />\n凍奶茶<br />\n<br />\n已經戒左兩個月左右<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n76減到而家61-63<br />\n階段勝利目標係55<br />\n我自己想落到40-45</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無做運動？ 帶氧加重訓<br />\n<br />\n否則戒一世口，一食即反彈</blockquote><br />\n有做<br />\n帶氧連續半年喇<br />\n<br />\n重訓去gym我要計下個支出先<br />\n<br />\n上網搵到d好出名的大陸人寫的書<br />\n講家居健身，心諗得唔得嫁<br />\n果條友幾出名下</blockquote><br />\n你用自己重量做 一樣有效果<br />\n屋企/公園都做得<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6efc2ac3d1822d44fe757a1e5302ee00ca2ac32","tid":273810,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:06:36.000Z","msg":"減肥喇"},{"pid":"a4604ec5b39f847327bbbda17b17c5fbba1b68b4","tid":273810,"uid":85742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:10:56.000Z","msg":"巴打你幾高?<br />\n減到45 已經過瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"940139e592ab830b13125499a2da1ec44fe6aa0d","tid":273810,"uid":67230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:12:21.000Z","msg":"分享下<br />\n我想由68減到62kg<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本身70，喱個星期戒食加游水，跑步<br />\n減左2，3kg"},{"pid":"e11971a06066003c0d4bd43cdebe39f520c0e5c1","tid":273810,"uid":45471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:33:58.000Z","msg":"我由82減到74，途中都係注意飲食，冇做運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申182"},{"pid":"dd882b780cedb2e16cb6ed78051ac52a79f6ed29","tid":273810,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T09:03:43.000Z","msg":"我都係62渣"}]}